WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.845
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.845 --> 00:00:03.515
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.515 --> 00:00:09.978
I'm going to deliver a pretty heavy word today; I hope you all are ready for this.

00:00:09.978 --> 00:00:14.710
I know I haven't been on much; I've been praying about this.

00:00:15.890 --> 00:00:25.160
As a Watchman, it's not always easy to come out and tell you all some of the things that I see, but it's my job, and I'm going to tell you what I see.

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:32.084
I prayed over this one for quite a while before delivering this because of how heavy this word is.

00:00:32.084 --> 00:00:56.640
I just feel like I should pray before I start because I want you to receive this; it is a very stern warning about things, and I was taken aback by it.

00:00:56.640 --> 00:01:05.410
So, let's just pray real quick and get right into it.

00:01:07.764 --> 00:01:19.400
Father, I thank You that You speak through my vocal cords and You think through my mind.

00:01:37.177 --> 00:01:40.109
I ask You for none of me and all of You.

00:01:40.109 --> 00:01:58.300
Every word that I say, Father, I thank You, Holy Spirit, that You help me to deliver it to Your people.

00:01:58.300 --> 00:02:21.479
Father, may this minister to them, and may they take it as the warning that You've given me about the end times and where we are.

00:02:21.479 --> 00:02:34.319
Father, I pray that they would take it to You in prayer and meditate on the Word.

00:02:50.099 --> 00:02:51.209
They won't get into fear; they will meditate on the Word and understand who they are in Christ.

00:02:51.209 --> 00:03:02.112
Lord, I just thank You in Jesus' name, Amen.

00:03:02.112 --> 00:03:06.053
Now, here comes the word.

00:03:06.053 --> 00:03:18.809
This is the urgency of what the Lord showed me.

00:03:18.809 --> 00:03:34.564
While I was praying, I put my prayer shawl on and went into deep intercession.

00:03:34.564 --> 00:04:07.020
All of a sudden, the Lord opened my eyes, and in the spirit realm, I was taken over and saw a meeting.

00:04:18.643 --> 00:04:23.880
I'm going to have to be very careful how I deliver this because of the things that I saw.

00:04:23.880 --> 00:05:17.783
I'm going to just say it like this: I want you all to read between the lines as much as possible, because things that I see could jeopardize me and put me in danger.

00:05:17.783 --> 00:05:30.354
So, let's just use a little wisdom here.

00:05:30.354 --> 00:05:53.920
I was taken up in the spirit and saw a meeting where they were contemplating the next virus.

00:05:55.685 --> 00:06:20.739
They were in a room, and I could see the heads of these leaders; I'll leave it at that.

00:06:22.380 --> 00:06:39.580
I won't say who I saw, but they were negotiating.

00:06:49.394 --> 00:06:52.360
The obesity epidemic across the world has reached heights beyond anybody's comprehension on purpose.

00:06:52.360 --> 00:07:04.725
Remember when I told you all I saw 350 million people perish?

00:07:04.725 --> 00:07:19.376
350 million would go home, but I didn't know how; I thought it was going to be a COVID-like thing.

00:07:19.376 --> 00:07:22.240
I saw a laboratory.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:32.313
I saw AI computer technology, and AI was creating a super-virus.

00:07:32.313 --> 00:07:46.770
They were using AI to create something more dangerous in the end times than COVID was.

00:08:04.253 --> 00:08:04.926
I could see DNA strands running like computer code.

00:08:04.926 --> 00:08:12.823
COVID was barely even used in this new strand.

00:08:31.906 --> 00:08:45.030
It was all over here, and they were taking lines from high blood pressure medicine, diabetes medicine, and splicing it into this virus, spanning off of obesity.

00:08:50.751 --> 00:08:50.996
It was being perfected.

00:08:50.996 --> 00:09:09.600
Skinny people who were not overweight, who took care of themselves, ate right, and maintained a good BMI, were safe.

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:22.293
They had immunities inside of them somehow to be able to sustain their bodies and not perish.

00:09:22.293 --> 00:09:42.960
But people who were on diabetic medicine, high blood pressure medicine, or high cholesterol medicines were targets.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:52.560
If you were heavy, you were a target throughout the whole world.

00:09:52.560 --> 00:10:14.950
I heard them say, 'Obesity is a drain on our economy; it's a drain on society; therefore, we must eliminate this.

00:10:14.950 --> 00:10:39.768
' I saw a plan to eliminate—and I'm going to be very careful—a group of people because the healthcare system is too much.

00:10:39.768 --> 00:11:01.260
I'm going to put a clip in right here that shows exactly what I saw—how much it's costing the healthcare system.

00:11:16.067 --> 00:11:23.120
The number of morbidly obese people across the United States has skyrocketed to over 30% in the last 20 years.

00:11:23.120 --> 00:11:31.885
What is obesity costing you and me, the taxpayer?

00:11:31.885 --> 00:11:40.880
Compared to other expenditures, it adds up quickly.

00:11:40.880 --> 00:11:53.780
Flying the president for one year in Air Force One costs us $500 million.

00:11:53.780 --> 00:12:09.653
All costs associated with illegal aliens in California alone cost taxpayers $9 billion a year.

00:12:10.628 --> 00:12:20.680
The 'No Child Left Behind' policy is a staggering $23 billion a year.

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:27.491
Drunk driving costs $24 billion a year.

00:12:27.491 --> 00:12:29.440
How does obesity stand up?

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:48.500
When you add up increased insurance costs, loss of work, and increased Medicare and Medicaid costs, it comes to $80 billion a year.

00:12:48.500 --> 00:12:54.417
That's more than all those other programs combined.

00:12:54.417 --> 00:12:59.305
Now, I saw Seven Deadly Sins.

00:13:14.215 --> 00:13:14.600
I saw Satan, and he was the head of the meeting.

00:13:26.135 --> 00:13:26.451
I saw a 'V' like Roman numeral five.

00:13:37.173 --> 00:13:37.480
At first, there were pillars, and I saw Seven Deadly Sins.

00:13:37.480 --> 00:13:46.564
I'm not familiar with this because I didn't realize this came from the Catholic Church; I'm studying this out before I present it.

00:13:46.564 --> 00:14:04.706
There were two pillars; five were all together—the things that people really recognize, like anger, lust, and wrath.

00:14:04.706 --> 00:14:26.719
I'm sorry, I'll butcher it since I don't have the verse in front of me, but these things the Lord hates: a lying spirit, a heart quick to shed innocent blood.

00:14:26.719 --> 00:14:34.275
Five went like this, and two were right here: slothfulness and gluttony.

00:14:34.275 --> 00:14:42.062
These were not as upfront as the other sins.

00:14:42.062 --> 00:14:56.777
In the spirit, I saw light shining on the five, but the devil pushed these two—gluttony and slothfulness—to the front to expose them because they weren't as bright.

00:14:56.777 --> 00:15:07.869
He was pushing them to the front, and then I saw him petitioning the Father because of Grace.

00:15:07.869 --> 00:15:25.519
There has been a grace over what we would consider a lack of concern, but there are many heavy people in the Body of Christ.

00:15:25.519 --> 00:15:47.034
He was calling forth all the scriptures, throwing them at the Father, and calling for judgment over obesity, saying this is an open door from seedtime and harvest.

00:15:47.034 --> 00:15:56.604
He was petitioning the open door for judgment concerning this.

00:15:58.589 --> 00:16:07.951
I'm a Watchman, and I'm here to tell you there is a plan for the enemy to design something to wipe people out.

00:16:07.951 --> 00:16:18.080
This is something else I thought was interesting: I saw them using bumblebees.

00:16:34.840 --> 00:16:35.280
These scientists were taking queen bees—big bees—and trying to figure out how to genetically alter them.

00:16:35.280 --> 00:16:37.829
Very strange, and I'm still praying over this.

00:16:39.690 --> 00:16:55.425
This genetic code using AI for this new thing will line up with the end-time Pale Horse rider.

00:16:55.425 --> 00:17:12.660
After I cried out for mercy, the Lord gave me more time and said, 'Brandon, get the weight off.

00:17:12.660 --> 00:17:32.860
' I have had a mandate by the Spirit of God to do whatever it takes to get this weight off and keep it off.

00:17:32.860 --> 00:17:42.844
I'm telling you all out of love; it's not to point fingers.

00:17:46.904 --> 00:17:47.208
I call for Grace.

00:17:47.208 --> 00:17:58.109
Father, forgive me and help me to get the weight off and take care of my body.

00:18:05.080 --> 00:18:05.399
I don't want to be bound by food addictions anymore.

00:18:07.533 --> 00:18:16.524
I have to reprogram my mind because the value meal at a Burger King or McDonald's was the standard.

00:18:16.524 --> 00:18:24.880
I had to ask myself: what is a right portion?

00:18:26.537 --> 00:18:31.345
I'm 43 years old and have no clue.

00:18:31.345 --> 00:18:35.285
I'm having to educate myself.

00:18:41.984 --> 00:18:44.960
Is six ounces of meat a day with lots of vegetables right?

00:18:56.253 --> 00:18:56.538
Some say carnivore, but I need to know what's good for me.

00:18:59.420 --> 00:18:59.785
This is serious.

00:19:03.609 --> 00:19:09.940
The average diet is 2,000 calories, but you have to eat less than that.

00:19:24.973 --> 00:19:31.640
I got a calorie app and was shocked; I was eating a ton every day, and that's how I got to be over 300 pounds.

00:19:33.280 --> 00:19:42.705
I'm trying to make this a lifestyle because the Spirit of God mandated it.

00:19:42.705 --> 00:19:49.737
The Lord said, 'You're out of time for what's coming.

00:19:49.737 --> 00:19:55.360
' I felt so much spiritual pressure.

00:19:55.360 --> 00:20:00.310
These 'bad guys' are crazy, just like Hitler was.

00:20:00.310 --> 00:20:05.799
They have a mandate to lower healthcare costs.

00:20:05.799 --> 00:20:14.720
I'm just trying to warn you and not put you in fear.

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:27.474
If you want to say I'm nuts, fine, but at least I told you.

00:20:27.474 --> 00:20:30.304
Jesus is coming.

00:20:30.304 --> 00:20:37.234
We're in the end of the end.

00:20:42.539 --> 00:20:43.159
The dark's getting darker, but the light's getting lighter.

00:20:43.159 --> 00:20:54.154
Jesus is in us, and we have nothing to fear.

00:21:06.280 --> 00:21:12.741
I'm believing God for supernatural healing for every one of you, that you'll be delivered from obesity and whatever they're trying to spice with this AI stuff.

00:21:13.159 --> 00:21:16.053
It's darker than people realize.

00:21:16.053 --> 00:21:34.530
Don't give up; get this weight off and take care of your bodies because for some of you, it will be life and death.

00:21:34.530 --> 00:21:44.177
We are not to fear because of Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

00:21:54.060 --> 00:22:01.840
But when the Lord petitions me to get 100 pounds off as quickly as possible, I listen.

00:22:13.857 --> 00:22:14.211
I saw this going into 2025.

00:22:16.099 --> 00:22:31.870
We are the Temple of the Holy Ghost, and He dwells on the inside of us.

00:22:31.870 --> 00:22:44.300
He has told me to get the 100 pounds off.

00:22:44.300 --> 00:22:56.703
I'm down 35 pounds, and my goal for March is another 20 to 30 pounds.

00:22:56.703 --> 00:23:14.780
I'm going to be the healthiest I've ever been, riding my bike and eating right.

00:23:14.780 --> 00:23:18.151
My blood pressure is perfect.

00:23:22.651 --> 00:23:28.950
The devil is legalistic; he knows the Bible better than we do.

00:23:28.950 --> 00:23:37.720
He’s not Holy Ghost-filled like us, but he knows the Word.

00:23:41.516 --> 00:23:44.737
I could hear him quoting gluttony scriptures.

00:23:44.737 --> 00:23:57.307
I was frozen in my tracks listening to him petition against me because I was obese.

00:23:57.307 --> 00:24:05.211
I pleaded the blood and took communion.

00:24:20.630 --> 00:24:20.900
The door was open because of seedtime and harvest, but Grace kept it from happening.

00:24:20.900 --> 00:24:30.289
This seedtime and harvest is going to accelerate beyond anything you can comprehend.

00:24:32.311 --> 00:24:43.676
The sower and the reaper are going to go hand-in-hand in any area of your life.

00:24:43.676 --> 00:24:49.413
It's the acceleration of seedtime and harvest.

00:24:49.413 --> 00:25:01.040
If you have an urgency to get the weight off, take care of your body.

00:25:01.040 --> 00:25:05.559
Father, I thank You for everyone listening.

00:25:21.804 --> 00:25:22.147
May this not bring fear but an urgency to take care of their temple.

00:25:22.147 --> 00:25:29.933
I thank You that they have wisdom and revelation knowledge.

00:25:39.892 --> 00:25:41.359
We break the spirit of addiction to junk food in the name of Jesus.

00:25:43.489 --> 00:25:47.419
We take authority over pastas, sweets, and cookies.

00:25:55.139 --> 00:25:58.347
Father, I thank You that we get the weight off and stay fit.

00:26:06.920 --> 00:26:07.360
I take authority over demonic spirits causing eating disorders.

00:26:07.360 --> 00:26:17.080
We command our minds and hormones to line up with the Word of God.

00:26:17.080 --> 00:26:20.860
We crucify our flesh daily.

00:26:20.860 --> 00:26:35.399
God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:26:35.399 --> 00:26:41.547
I pray blessings and healing over your bodies.

00:26:45.800 --> 00:26:46.027
You are healed and whole.

00:26:49.410 --> 00:26:52.700
I call you delivered from addictions, from drugs to alcohol to lust.

00:26:52.700 --> 00:26:59.279
You don't have to be bound by the devil.

00:27:12.729 --> 00:27:15.605
We call forth freedom in the name of Jesus.

00:27:23.140 --> 00:27:23.440
We call for Grace and Mercy.

00:27:23.440 --> 00:27:30.159
Thank you for being part of this video.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
If you could click that notification bell, it would bless us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Thank you for liking and subscribing.

